a></p>","hasStoryPackage":"true","body":"<p>When Gérard Depardieu failed to materialise for the UK premiere of Welcome to New York at the Edinburgh festival on 28 June, no one was especially surprised. After all, the man has a busy schedule shuttling between Belgium and Russia, the two countries that have given him sanctuary outside his native France, which include <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/mar/25/gerard-depardieu-cvstos-watches-proud-to-be-russian\">endorsing a line of patriotic, pro-Russian watches</a>.</p><p>Now it turns out Depardieu had made it to Scotland, but became otherwise detained after an enthusiastic visit to the Hotel Eilean Iarmain bar at Isleornsay on the Sleat peninsula on  Skye. Photographs emerged on Twitter of Depardieu sinking pints of beer and tucking into haggis on 27 June, the day before the film screening.</p>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SiobhanSynnot/statuses/482985423678230529\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Great chieftain of the Pudding Race...meeting a Skye haggis  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nodepartureforDepardieu?src=hash\">#nodepartureforDepardieu</a> <a href=\"http://t.co/GoFrE0cwtG\">pic.twitter.com/GoFrE0cwtG</a></p>&mdash; Siobhan Synnot (@SiobhanSynnot) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SiobhanSynnot/statuses/482985423678230529\">June 28, 2014</a></blockquote>  </figure>  <p>Depardieu's companions in the pub were confirmed on Monday as  Rody Gorman, a Gaelic poet, as well as Depardieu's personal chef.</p>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SiobhanSynnot/statuses/482996911096741888\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gibbzer\">@gibbzer</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bettybluetoyou\">@bettybluetoyou</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/edfilmfest\">@edfilmfest</a> I&#39;d like to think we&#39;d all been there in more flattering tops <a href=\"http://t.co/VnnFPnrjQl\">pic.twitter.com/VnnFPnrjQl</a></p>&mdash; Siobhan Synnot (@SiobhanSynnot) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SiobhanSynnot/statuses/482996911096741888\">June 28, 2014</a></blockquote>  </figure>  <p><a href=\"http://www.edinburghnews.scotsman.com/news/gerard-depardieu-snubs-film-festival-for-skye-pint-1-3460850\">Speaking to the Scotsman</a>, a representative of the Edinburgh festival said: “He has let the festival down very badly ... We won’t be pursuing this any further because the screening has already taken place – but there is some annoyance here.”</p><p><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/world/2011/aug/17/gerard-depardieu-delayed-flight-passenger?guni=Article:in%20body%20link\">• Gérard Depardieu accused of urinating on a plane</a><br></p>","headline":"Gérard Depardieu ducks out of Edinburgh film festival appearance after drinking session in Skye pub","trailText":"Actor was due to attend UK premiere of Dominique Strauss-Kahn drama Welcome to New York, but failed to turn up<br><br>","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/6/30/1404126651936/61c482fb-6908-46eb-8268-b3621d66038a-140x84.jpeg","wordcount":"224","commentable":"true","byline":"Andrew Pulver","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-07-03T12:30:00+01:00"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jun/30/gerard-depardieu-edinburgh-film-festival-skye-pub","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/film/2014/jun/30/gerard-depardieu-edinburgh-film-festival-skye-pub","tags":[{"id":"film/gerard-depardieu","webTitle":"Gérard Depardieu","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","sectionName":"Film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/gerard-depardieu","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/film/gerard-depardieu","references":[]},{"id":"film/edinburghfilmfestival","webTitle":"Edinburgh film festival","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","sectionName":"Film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/edinburghfilmfestiv