en invited.</p><p>Blair's 1997 party attracted high-flying British celebrities like Oasis guitarist Noel Gallagher, but was later seen to backfire on the then PM as invited stars later criticised his government.</p>","headline":"Cumberbatch and Harrison Ford top Cameron's Cool Britannia revival","trailText":"<p>Stellar cast invited to celebrate achievements of Britain's creative industries at publicly funded Foreign Office bash</p>","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/6/30/1404111492344/Benedict-Cumberbatch-006.jpg","wordcount":"222","commentable":"true","byline":"Press Association","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-07-03T07:07:00Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2014/jun/30/david-cameron-cool-britannia-harrison-ford-benedict-cumberbatch","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/politics/2014/jun/30/david-cameron-cool-britannia-harrison-ford-benedict-cumberbatch","tags":[{"id":"film/film","webTitle":"Film","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","sectionName":"Film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/film","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/film/film","references":[]},{"id":"culture/culture","webTitle":"Culture","type":"keyword","sectionId":"culture","sectionName":"Culture","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/culture/culture","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/culture/culture","references":[]},{"id":"politics/davidcameron","webTitle":"David Cameron","type":"keyword","sectionId":"politics","sectionName":"Politics","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/politics/davidcameron","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/politics/davidcameron","references":[]},{"id":"uk/uk","webTitle":"UK news","type":"keyword","sectionId":"uk-news","sectionName":"UK news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk/uk","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/uk/uk","references":[]},{"id":"culture/benedict-cumberbatch","webTitle":"Benedict Cumberbatch","